description: These are the jet veto maps for ['Winter22Run3_RunCD_V1', 'Winter22Run3_RunE_V1']. The recommended veto maps to be applied to both data and MC for analysis is 'jetvetomap'.

corrections.name: Winter22Run3_RunCD_V1
corrections.description: These are the jet veto maps showing regions with an excess of jets (hot zones) and lack of jets (cold zones). Using the phi-symmetry of the CMS detector, these areas with detector and or calibration issues can be pinpointed.

inputs.name: type
inputs.description: name of the type of veto map. The recommended map for analyses is 'jetvetomap'.

output.name: vetomaps
output.description: Non-zero value for (eta, phi) indicates that the region is vetoed.
